{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/146/comments/90379063.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo:fd26e4f96e41..4957acb1df7a?path=src%2FFactory.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/146/_/diff#comment-90379063"}}, "parent": {"id": 90352462, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/146/comments/90352462.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/146/_/diff#comment-90352462"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 146, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/146.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/146"}}, "title": "[A-5] Add imu sensor"}, "content": {"raw": "You could get the world entity:\n\n`auto worldEntity = _ecm.EntityByComponents<components::World>();`\n\nThen get the gravity:\n\n`auto gravity = _ecm.Component<components::Gravity>(worldEntity)->Data();`\n\nOr, since the IMU plugin is attached to the world, you could get `worldEntity` at the `Configure` callback and store it, since it shouldn't change.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>You could get the world entity:</p>\n<p><code>auto worldEntity = _ecm.EntityByComponents&lt;components::World&gt;();</code></p>\n<p>Then get the gravity:</p>\n<p><code>auto gravity = _ecm.Component&lt;components::Gravity&gt;(worldEntity)-&gt;Data();</code></p>\n<p>Or, since the IMU plugin is attached to the world, you could get <code>worldEntity</code> at the <code>Configure</code> callback and store it, since it shouldn't change.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-02-04T21:33:19.350889+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded